PI-STRAP
========

Pi-Strap is a Raspberry Pi statistics class written in PHP and presented using
Twitter Bootstrap.

Installation
------------

The piStrap.php class must be included into your PHP file: 
require('lib/_piStrap.php');

Create a new piStrap instance:
$stats = new piStrap;

Access Pi data:
$info =  $stats->generalStats();
$user =  $stats->userStats();
etc..

Basic loop to access data:
foreach($info as $key => $value) {
     echo $key.": ".$value;
}
